Package syntax

Class TokenIterator

java.lang.Object
syntax.TokenIterator
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterator<Token>
final class TokenIterator extends Object implements Iterator<Token>
This iterator allows to tokenize provided character sequence and traverse through tokens.
